headline.main: Maine's Biggest Dog Sled Race Celebrates 25th Anniversary
headline.print_headline: Maine's Biggest Dog Sled Race Celebrates 25th Anniversary

lead_paragraph: British anti-doping authorities condemned the leaking of information "which only serves to fuel rumor and innuendo" on Saturday after the latest media report surrounding athlete Mo Farah and his American coach Alberto Salazar.
